{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.600", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Liberalen jetzt auch wieder hier im Parlament sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen m\u00f6chte ich noch einmal ganz klar sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leistung muss sich wieder lohnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus diesem Grunde ist meine Partei der Meinung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir dringend die Verm\u00f6gensteuer wieder einf\u00fchren m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.760", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht nur der Soziologe Sighard Neckel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Deutschland auf dem besten Weg in einen oligarchischen Kapitalismus sieht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.080", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch mein Kollege Gerhard Schick hat dazu ein Buch geschrieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem von \u201eMachtwirtschaft\u201c\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht von Marktwirtschaft\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Rede ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.520", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist die Situation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in die wir mehr und mehr hineinrutschen in Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.400", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben einen Kapitalismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem leider Erbschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heirat und gro\u00dfe Verm\u00f6gen und eben nicht Talent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht Bildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht pers\u00f6nlicher Einsatz zum Erfolg f\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.360", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kurz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist ein Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.560", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem sich Leistung nicht mehr wirklich lohnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil in Deutschland die soziale Herkunft \u00fcber Lebenschancen entscheidet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das liegt nicht daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Steuern so hoch sind und die sogenannten Leistungstr\u00e4ger am Ende des Monats zu wenig auf ihrem Konto haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern es liegt ganz zentral daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.400", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Verm\u00f6gensbesteuerung in Deutschland viel zu niedrig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um der Spaltung in Arm und Reich entgegenzuwirken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.240", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es liegt daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.280", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es sich leisten k\u00f6nnten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu wenig dazu beitragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.120", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unser Gemeinwesen zu finanzieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.000", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit zum Beispiel Alleinerziehende dabei unterst\u00fctzt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Familien vor Armut und Ausgrenzung zu bewahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit unsere Kinder nicht l\u00e4nger in maroden Schulen unterrichtet werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.080", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit jeder und jede unabh\u00e4ngig vom Geldbeutel der Eltern studieren kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen nicht l\u00e4nger zulassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Teile unserer Gesellschaft abgeh\u00e4ngt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend das Verm\u00f6gen von anderen ins Unermessliche steigt und eigentlich nur noch die Mittelschicht in Deutschland Steuern zahlt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht erst seit der Ver\u00f6ffentlichung des F\u00fcnften Armuts- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Reichtumsberichts wissen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.920", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich mehr als die H\u00e4lfte des gesamten Nettoverm\u00f6gens in Deutschland in den H\u00e4nden der reichsten 10\u00a0Prozent befindet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir aber leider nicht wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie genau dieses Verm\u00f6gen sich innerhalb des obersten Dezils verteilt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.000", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist aus unserer Sicht ein weiterer wichtiger Grund f\u00fcr die Wiedereinf\u00fchrung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.040", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kann nicht sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.800", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir von Hartz-IV-Empf\u00e4ngern oder Aufstockern verlangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre gesamten Verm\u00f6gensverh\u00e4ltnisse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.800", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sogar ihre Lebensverh\u00e4ltnisse bis in das kleinste Detail offenzulegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.280", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend der Staat bei den Verm\u00f6gensverh\u00e4ltnissen der Superreichen wirklich vollkommen und komplett im Dunkeln tappt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.400", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen w\u00e4re die Einf\u00fchrung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer ein wichtiger Schritt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die katastrophale Datenlage im Bereich der Hochverm\u00f6genden zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es w\u00fcrde es schwerer machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besitz und das Einkommen daraus vor dem Fiskus zu verstecken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel in Steueroasen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.960", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir es endlich schaffen w\u00fcrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kluft zwischen Arm und Reich kleiner statt immer gr\u00f6\u00dfer werden zu lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so empfehlen es uns \u00fcbrigens auch die OECD und der IWF\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.120", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4re sogar unsere wirtschaftliche Entwicklung in Deutschland besser. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die OECD sagt konkret, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Steigerung beim deutschen Bruttoinlandsprodukt wegen der gestiegenen Ungleichheit seit 1985 um 6\u00a0Prozent geringer ausgefallen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als wenn wir mehr Gerechtigkeit in Deutschland h\u00e4tten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen m\u00fcssen wir dringend gegensteuern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus unserer Sicht ist die Verm\u00f6gensteuer ein wichtiger Baustein f\u00fcr mehr Gerechtigkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Sicherung der \u00f6kologisch-sozialen Marktwirtschaft in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr eine bessere wirtschaftliche Entwicklung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb geh\u00f6rt sie weiterhin auf die politische Tagesordnung in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.000", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat der Abgeordnete Hans Michelbach f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}